								p.testimonial-bio-source Jay Fairfield, Chairman &amp; CEO
								h5.testimonial-bio-company Honda Logistics
								p.testimonial-bio-quote "We have worked with Curt since 2012 and he has helped negotiate two new leases.  Each time he understood our need to be in a specific geographic area and knew there were limited options that would fit our requirement.  He completed an extensive search, organized the data, and prepared it so it was easy for me to review.  Once a building was chosen, he assisted in the lease negotiation.  His market knowledge is invaluable and key to us feeling confident in our decisions.  I would be happy to recommend him to anyone with industrial needs in the area."
